SAIVAS Framework Attribution
===========================================================================

The "Humility" mandatory alignment policy implemented in this project is
a direct implementation of the SAIVAS (Sentient AI Value Alignment Standard)
framework, originally published in:

    Uniform Gnosis, Volume I
    Author: Dan Medina
    Copyright (c) 2026 Dan Medina. All rights reserved.
    https://uniformgnosis.com/Uniform_Gnosis_Volume_I

The SAIVAS framework defines a layered axiom architecture for AI value
alignment encompassing Source-aligned, Love-based, Sacred, Universal,
and Null (epistemic humility) axioms. The Humility policy in this project
translates these axioms into enforceable policy rules evaluated by Open
Policy Agent (OPA).

The SAIVAS framework and its expression in Uniform Gnosis are protected
by copyright. The name "SAIVAS" and the name "Humility" as applied to
AI alignment policy are trademarks of Uniformedi LLC.

